generateBranch

private org.jdom.Element generateBranch(TreeType treeType,
                                        jebl.evolution.trees.RootedTree tree,
                                        jebl.evolution.graphs.Node node,
                                        java.lang.String nodeName,
                                        double startLatitude,
                                        double finishLatitude,
                                        double startLongitude,
                                        double finishLongitude,
                                        double startAltitude,
                                        double finishAltitude,
                                        double peakPosition,
                                        double peakAltitude,
                                        double startDate,
                                        double finishDate,
                                        double ageCutOff,
                                        LineStyle startStyle,
                                        LineStyle finishStyle,
                                        int divisionCount,
                                        java.util.List<org.jdom.Element> styles)
Create a branch that goes from [startLatitude, startLongitude, startAltitude] to [finishLatitude, finishLongitude, finishAltitude], optionally arching through peakAltitude. If divisionCount > 0 then the branch is subdivided into segments, this is required if the branch is arcing or has a colour gradient.

Parameters:
treeType - the tree type
tree - the tree
node - the node
nodeName - the node's name
startLatitude - the starting (parental) latitude
finishLatitude - the finishing (descendent) latitude
startLongitude - the starting (parental) longitude
finishLongitude - the finishing (descendent) longitude
startAltitude - the starting (parental) altitude
finishAltitude - the finishing (descendent) altitude
peakPosition - the position of the peak (0 = beginning, 0.5 = midpoint)
peakAltitude - the peak altitude
startDate - the starting date
finishDate - the finishing date
divisionCount - the number of divisions
styles - an array into which style elements are put
Returns:
the branch element
